<h3>What is Online Distance Learning?</h3>

	<ul class="sub_list">
    <li>You can study a structured course with the flexibility to choose your own time and place to study.</li>
   <li>You will be supported by a personal tutor who will give you guidance and advice about your course and assignments.</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Where and How do I Study?</h3>

	<p>Learning from home or work gives you the freedom to:</p>
	<ul class="sub_list">
    <li>work at your own pace - to slow down, speed up, stop, start again - in response to changes in your circumstances;</li>
    <li>plan your studies to suit your home, social, and work circumstances;</li>
    <li>study where it is most convenient for you - at home, at work, at a local library, on journeys;</li>
    <li>study at a time to suit you - when you choose - at any time of the day and night, and any day of the week.</li>
	</ul>

	
	<h3>Who Studies by Online Distance Learning?</h3>

	<p>The opportunity to study at home appeals to many types of people:</p>
	<ul class="sub_list">
    <li>High school leavers who need to start work</li>
    <li>Graduates starting their careers</li>
    <li>Mature people who have delayed entry into further education</li>
    <li>Older people who have work or family commitments which prevent studying full-time</li>
    <li>Those thinking of continuing education for personal development or for a career change</li>
    <li>Those who want to upgrade their professional qualifications</li>
    <li>Service men and women in the armed forces who regularly move locations.</li>
	</ul>
   
	

	<p>The benefits to you will be that you will:</p>
	<ul class="sub_list">
    <li>gain a valuable qualification;</li>
    <li>be more successful in your work;</li>
    <li>manage workplace problems more effectively;</li>
    <li>have better chances of promotion;</li>
    </ul>

	<p>All of our courses:</p>
	<ul class="sub_list">
    <li>will help you to use your learning to improve your performance and progress in your career;</li>
    <li>are of reasonable cost; </li>
    <li>give you a fast return on investment by helping you progress;</li>
    <li>help you to grow and develop personally.</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>We Help You to Build a Successful Future</h3>
	<ul class="sub_list">
    <li>By gaining a qualification</li>
    <li>By sharpening your workplace skills</li>
    <li>By learning more about essential tools and techniques</li>
    <li>By improving your understanding and knowledge.</li>
	</ul>
